{"title":"海誓（四首）","authors":["宫玺"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":3,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海誓（四首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宫玺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脱下毛蓝布褂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿上崭新的军衣；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国啊，今天起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是您忠实的战士！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告别家乡的平原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离开金色的大陆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背起背包，迈大步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏上蓝色的土地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝色的土地呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多少岛屿多少珍珠？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我奉祖国的命令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去把海疆守护！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船儿出海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬起帆篷；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海鸥赶来欢迎我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始战斗的人生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水波的征途啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一半浪，一半风；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪，是暴烈的野马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风，是无形的缰绳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然晕吐一千次，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也吓不倒我这新兵；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要驾驭它、制服它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在风波路上纵横驰骋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海誓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辽阔的大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"环抱着大陆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"环抱大陆的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是人民战士。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士的意志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是海的意志；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个波浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个个胸脯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茫茫大海中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一滴水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献身为祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗永不息！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上日出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星期天，早晨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上风波，天边烟云；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轻的战士小岛上坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么书吸住了他的心？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借这明丽的曙光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借这清新的时辰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读着毛主席的书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像青竹吸着水分。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一句——一道霞光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一页——一片朝暾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扯平了风波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱散了烟云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轻的战士神情专注，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知朝霞已披了一身；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手捧着那本金色的书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海上升起红日一轮……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}